{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846809076,"sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","part":{"id":"prt_d78b7d9b6001dCYJj17GFoeMhm","messageID":"msg_d78b7c4f50019W3bXKuS3X5eav","sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c129cf4e19364ba08c0dd5d6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: 实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，作为基于 controller-runtime 的 Kubernetes 控制器，负责 watch `Sandbox` CR（`agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）并根据 `last-activity-time` 注解自动清理空闲沙箱。与 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager`（基于 Redis Store 轮询）形成双层清理保障，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲检测能力。\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Package Layout\n10: \n11: ```\n12: cmd/agentd/\n13: └── main.go              — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\n14: pkg/agentd/\n15: ├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile + SetupWithManager\n16: ├── reconciler_test.go   — 单元测试（fake client）\n17: └── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\n18: pkg/workloadmanager/\n19: └── const.go             — LastActivityAnnotationKey 常量（新增）\n20: ```\n21: \n22: ### 1.3 Data Flow\n23: \n24: ```\n25: Kubernetes API Server\n26:     │\n27:     ├── Sandbox Create/Update/Delete Event\n28:     │       │\n29:     │       ▼\n30:     │   controller-runtime Informer (cache)\n31:     │       │\n32:     │       ▼\n33:     │   Reconciler.Reconcile(ctx, req)\n34:     │       │\n35:     │       ├── 1. Get Sandbox by NamespacedName\n36:     │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n37:     │       │       └── Error  → return (Result{}, err)\n38:     │       │\n39:     │       ├── 2. Read annotation \"last-activity-time\"\n40:     │       │       └── Missing/empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n41:     │       │\n42:     │       ├── 3. Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n43:     │       │       └── Parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n44:     │       │\n45:     │       ├── 4. Compute expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n46:     │       │\n47:     │       └── 5. Check expiration\n48:     │               ├── now.After(expirationTime)\n49:     │               │       ├── Delete(sandbox)\n50:     │               │       │       ├── NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n51:     │               │       │       ├── Error    → return (Result{}, err)\n52:     │               │       │       └── Success  → return (Result{}, nil)\n53:     │               │\n54:     │               └── !now.After(expirationTime)\n55:     │                       └── return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n56:     │\n57:     └── WorkloadManager LifecycleManager（独立运行，负责 TTL/孤儿/幽灵清理）\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ### 1.4 Dependencies\n61: \n62: | Dependency | Purpose | Type |\n63: |---|---|---|\n64: | `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | Manager、Reconciler 模式、workqueue | Direct |\n65: | `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD 类型定义 | Direct |\n66: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | `errors.IsNotFound` 判断 | Direct |\n67: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | Scheme 注册 | Direct |\n68: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime` | `utilruntime.Must` 安全初始化 | Direct |\n69: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 常量引用 | Internal |\n70: \n71: ## 2. Data Structures\n72: \n73: ### 2.1 Constants\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: // pkg/agentd/const.go\n77: package agentd\n78: \n79: import \"time\"\n80: \n81: // SessionExpirationTimeout is the fixed idle expiration threshold.\n82: // A Sandbox is considered expired when its last activity time plus\n83: // this duration has elapsed.\n84: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n85: ```\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // pkg/workloadmanager/const.go (new file)\n89: package workloadmanager\n90: \n91: // LastActivityAnnotationKey is the annotation key used to store the\n92: // last activity timestamp on Sandbox objects. The value is an RFC3339\n93: // formatted timestamp updated by the Router on each proxied request.\n94: const LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n95: ```\n96: \n97: ### 2.2 Reconciler\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: // pkg/agentd/reconciler.go\n101: package agentd\n102: \n103: import (\n104:     \"context\"\n105:     \"time\"\n106: \n107:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n108:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n109:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n110:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n111:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n112: )\n113: \n114: // Reconciler implements the idle cleanup controller for Sandbox resources.\n115: // It embeds client.Client for API server operations and holds a Scheme\n116: // for type registration.\n117: type Reconciler struct {\n118:     client.Client\n119:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n120: }\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### 2.3 Sentinel Errors\n124: \n125: 无自定义 sentinel errors。所有错误来源于：\n126: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors.IsNotFound(err)` — 资源不存在\n127: - `time.Parse` 返回的解析错误 — 时间戳格式非法\n128: - controller-runtime 返回的网络/API 错误 — 重试由框架处理\n129: \n130: ### 2.4 Key Constants Reference\n131: \n132: | Constant | Value | Defined In | Used By |\n133: |---|---|---|---|\n134: | `SessionExpirationTimeout` | `15 * time.Minute` | `pkg/agentd/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` |\n135: | `LastActivityAnnotationKey` | `\"last-activity-time\"` | `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`, `pkg/router/`, `pkg/workloadmanager/` |\n136: \n137: ## 3. API Contracts\n138: \n139: 本控制器不暴露 HTTP API。与 Kubernetes API Server 的交互通过 controller-runtime client 完成。\n140: \n141: ### 3.1 Watched Resources\n142: \n143: | API Group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n144: |---|---|---|---|\n145: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Create, Update, Delete（controller-runtime `For()` 默认行为） |\n146: \n147: ### 3.2 Reconcile Contract\n148: \n149: **Input:** `ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request`\n150: \n151: **Output:** `(ctrl.Result, error)`\n152: \n153: | Condition | Result | Error | Side Effect |\n154: |---|---|---|---|\n155: | Sandbox NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n156: | Get error (non-NotFound) | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n157: | Annotation missing/empty | `{}` | `nil` | None |\n158: | Timestamp parse error | `{RequeueAfter: 30s}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n159: | Not expired | `{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}` | `nil` | None |\n160: | Expired, Delete NotFound | `{}` | `nil` | None (already deleted) |\n161: | Expired, Delete error | `{}` | `err` | None (retry) |\n162: | Expired, Delete success | `{}` | `nil` | Sandbox deleted |\n163: \n164: ### 3.3 Manager Configuration\n165: \n166: | Option | Value | Rationale |\n167: |---|---|---|\n168: | `Scheme` | core + `sandboxv1alpha1` | 支持 Sandbox 类型操作 |\n169: | `Metrics.BindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 metrics 服务 |\n170: | `HealthProbeBindAddress` | `\"0\"` | S 级简化，禁用 health probe |\n171: | Signal handler | `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` | SIGTERM/SIGINT 优雅关闭 |\n172: \n173: ## 4. Core Implementation\n174: \n175: ### 4.1 Reconcile Method\n176: \n177: ```go\n178: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n179:     sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n180:     if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n181:         if errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n182:             return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n183:         }\n184:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n185:     }\n186: \n187:     lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n188:     if !exists || lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n189:         return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n190:     }\n191: \n192:     lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n193:     if err != nil {\n194:         return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err\n195:     }\n196: \n197:     expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n198: \n199:     if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n200:         if err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox); err != nil && !errors.IsNotFound(err) {\n201:             return ctrl.Result{}, err\n202:         }\n203:         return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n204:     }\n205: \n206:     return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil\n207: }\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### 4.2 SetupWithManager\n211: \n212: ```go\n213: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n214:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n215:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n216:         Complete(r)\n217: }\n218: ```\n219: \n220: ### 4.3 Binary Entry Point\n221: \n222: ```go\n223: // cmd/agentd/main.go\n224: package main\n225: \n226: import (\n227:     \"flag\"\n228:     \"os\"\n229: \n230:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n231:     utilruntime \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime\"\n232:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n233:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"\n234:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/log/zap\"\n235:     metricsserver \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/metrics/server\"\n236: \n237:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n238: )\n239: \n240: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n241: \n242: func init() {\n243:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n244:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n245: }\n246: \n247: func main() {\n248:     opts := zap.Options{\n249:         Development: true,\n250:     }\n251:     opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)\n252:     flag.Parse()\n253: \n254:     ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))\n255: \n256:     mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n257:         Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n258:         Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n259:         HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n260:     })\n261:     if err != nil {\n262:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to start manager\")\n263:         os.Exit(1)\n264:     }\n265: \n266:     if err := (&agentd.Reconciler{\n267:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n268:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n269:     }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n270:         setupLog.Error(err, \"unable to create controller\", \"controller\", \"Sandbox\")\n271:         os.Exit(1)\n272:     }\n273: \n274:     setupLog.Info(\"starting manager\")\n275:     if err := mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n276:         setupLog.Error(err, \"problem running manager\")\n277:         os.Exit(1)\n278:     }\n279: }\n280: \n281: var setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")\n282: ```\n283: \n284: ### 4.4 Reconcile Decision Tree\n285: \n286: ```\n287: Reconcile(ctx, req)\n288: ├── Get(req.NamespacedName)\n289: │   ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)          [已删除，无需处理]\n290: │   └── Error    → return ({}, err)           [API 错误，重试]\n291: │\n292: ├── Annotations[LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n293: │   ├── Missing   → return ({}, nil)          [无活动时间，跳过]\n294: │   └── Empty     → return ({}, nil)          [空值，跳过]\n295: │\n296: ├── time.Parse(RFC3339, value)\n297: │   └── Error → return ({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)  [格式异常，30s 后重试]\n298: │\n299: ├── expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min\n300: │\n301: └── time.Now().After(expirationTime)\n302:     ├── true (expired)\n303:     │   └── Delete(sandbox)\n304:     │       ├── NotFound → return ({}, nil)   [已被其他控制器删除]\n305:     │       ├── Error    → return ({}, err)    [删除失败，重试]\n306:     │       └── Success  → return ({}, nil)    [删除成功]\n307:     │\n308:     └── false (not expired)\n309:         └── return ({RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n310: ```\n311: \n312: ### 4.5 Time Precision Considerations\n313: \n314: - `time.Until(expirationTime)` 返回 `time.Duration`，在过期时刻临近时趋近于 0\n315: - controller-runtime 对 `RequeueAfter: 0` 的处理等同于立即 requeue，不会导致 busy loop\n316: - 当 `time.Now()` 恰好等于 `expirationTime` 时，`After()` 返回 `false`，下一次 requeue 会在下一个调度周期触发\n317: \n318: ## 5. Error Handling\n319: \n320: ### 5.1 Error Classification\n321: \n322: | Error Source | Error Type | Handling Strategy |\n323: |---|---|---|\n324: | `r.Get` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，不重试 |\n325: | `r.Get` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n326: | `time.Parse` | Format error | 返回 `({RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`，固定 30s 后重试 |\n327: | `r.Delete` — NotFound | `apierrors.IsNotFound` | 静默返回 `({}, nil)`，幂等处理 |\n328: | `r.Delete` — 其他 | Network/API error | 返回 `({}, err)`，controller-runtime workqueue 指数退避重试 |\n329: \n330: ### 5.2 Idempotency Guarantees\n331: \n332: - **Delete 幂等**：多次调用 `Delete` 对同一 Sandbox 不会产生副作用，`IsNotFound` 视为成功\n333: - **Reconcile 幂等**：同一 Sandbox 的多次 reconcile 调用不会产生重复删除\n334: - **与 LifecycleManager 共存**：两者可能同时尝试删除同一 Sandbox，`IsNotFound` 处理确保双方均正常完成\n335: \n336: ### 5.3 Error Propagation\n337: \n338: - 解析错误（`time.Parse`）返回给 controller-runtime，记录到日志但不会导致控制器崩溃\n339: - API 错误由 controller-runtime 的 workqueue 管理重试，自动指数退避\n340: - 不会 panic，所有错误路径都有明确的返回值\n341: \n342: ## 6. Testing Strategy\n343: \n344: ### 6.1 Unit Test Matrix\n345: \n346: | Test Case | Sandbox Exists | Annotation | Timestamp | Time vs Expiration | Expected Result |\n347: |---|---|---|---|---|---|\n348: | `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound` | No (Get NotFound) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n349: | `TestReconcile_GetError` | No (Get error) | — | — | — | `Result{}`, `err` |\n350: | `TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing` | Yes | Missing | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n351: | `TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty` | Yes | `\"\"` | — | — | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n352: | `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp` | Yes | `\"not-a-timestamp\"` | Parse fails | — | `Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}`, `err` |\n353: | `TestReconcile_NotExpired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 5 min ago | `now < expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}`, `nil` |\n354: | `TestReconcile_Expired` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | Delete called, `Result{}`, `nil` |\n355: | `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound` | Yes (Delete NotFound) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `nil` |\n356: | `TestReconcile_DeleteError` | Yes (Delete error) | Valid RFC3339 | 20 min ago | `now > expiration` | `Result{}`, `err` |\n357: | `TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary` | Yes | Valid RFC3339 | Exactly 15 min ago | `now == expiration` | `Result{RequeueAfter: >=0}`, `nil` |\n358: \n359: ### 6.2 Test Helpers\n360: \n361: ```go\n362: // 使用 controller-runtime fake client\n363: import (\n364:     \"context\"\n365:     \"testing\"\n366:     \"time\"\n367: \n368:     \"github.com/stretchr/testify/assert\"\n369:     \"github.com/stretchr/testify/require\"\n370:     sandboxv1alpha1 \"sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1\"\n371:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n372:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n373:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n374:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/types\"\n375:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake\"\n376:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n377: \n378:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd\"\n379:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n380: )\n381: \n382: func newTestScheme() *runtime.Scheme {\n383:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n384:     _ = sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n385:     return scheme\n386: }\n387: \n388: func newFakeReconciler(objects ...runtime.Object) *agentd.Reconciler {\n389:     return &agentd.Reconciler{\n390:         Client: fake.NewClientBuilder().\n391:             WithScheme(newTestScheme()).\n392:             WithRuntimeObjects(objects...).\n393:             Build(),\n394:         Scheme: newTestScheme(),\n395:     }\n396: }\n397: \n398: func newSandbox(ns, name string, annotations map[string]string) *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox {\n399:     return &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{\n400:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n401:             Namespace:   ns,\n402:             Name:        name,\n403:             Annotations: annotations,\n404:         },\n405:     }\n406: }\n407: ```\n408: \n409: ### 6.3 Mock Strategy\n410: \n411: - **Fake Client**：使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client/fake` 模拟 Kubernetes API Server\n412: - **时间控制**：测试中通过构造不同的 `last-activity-time` 值和依赖 `time.Now()` 的相对计算来覆盖过期/未过期分支\n413: - **Error Injection**：fake client 不支持直接注入 Get/Delete 错误，可通过自定义 `client.Client` wrapper 或使用 `WithStatusSubresource` 等 builder 选项模拟\n414: \n415: ### 6.4 Test File Structure\n416: \n417: ```go\n418: // pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go\n419: \n420: func TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\n421: func TestReconcile_GetError(t *testing.T) { ... }\n422: func TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing(t *testing.T) { ... }\n423: func TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty(t *testing.T) { ... }\n424: func TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp(t *testing.T) { ... }\n425: func TestReconcile_NotExpired(t *testing.T) { ... }\n426: func TestReconcile_Expired(t *testing.T) { ... }\n427: func TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound(t *testing.T) { ... }\n428: func TestReconcile_DeleteError(t *testing.T) { ... }\n429: func TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary(t *testing.T) { ... }\n430: \n431: func TestSetupWithManager(t *testing.T) { ... }\n432: ```\n433: \n434: ### 6.5 Gate Requirements\n435: \n436: - `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` — 无告警\n437: - `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` — 全部通过\n438: - `go mod tidy` — 无变更\n439: \n440: ## 7. Deployment Considerations\n441: \n442: ### 7.1 Deployment Manifest\n443: \n444: agentd 作为独立的 Deployment 部署在集群中：\n445: \n446: ```yaml\n447: apiVersion: apps/v1\n448: kind: Deployment\n449: metadata:\n450:   name: agentd\n451:   namespace: agentcube-system\n452: spec:\n453:   replicas: 1\n454:   selector:\n455:     matchLabels:\n456:       app: agentd\n457:   template:\n458:     metadata:\n459:       labels:\n460:         app: agentd\n461:     spec:\n462:       serviceAccountName: agentd\n463:       containers:\n464:       - name: agentd\n465:         image: agentcube/agentd:latest\n466:         resources:\n467:           requests:\n468:             cpu: 50m\n469:             memory: 64Mi\n470:           limits:\n471:             cpu: 200m\n472:             memory: 128Mi\n473: ---\n474: apiVersion: v1\n475: kind: ServiceAccount\n476: metadata:\n477:   name: agentd\n478:   namespace: agentcube-system\n479: ---\n480: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n481: kind: ClusterRole\n482: metadata:\n483:   name: agentd\n484: rules:\n485: - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n486:   resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n487:   verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n488: ---\n489: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n490: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n491: metadata:\n492:   name: agentd\n493: roleRef:\n494:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n495:   kind: ClusterRole\n496:   name: agentd\n497: subjects:\n498: - kind: ServiceAccount\n499:   name: agentd\n500:   namespace: agentcube-system\n501: ```\n502: \n503: ### 7.2 RBAC Requirements\n504: \n505: | API Group | Resource | Verbs | Purpose |\n506: |---|---|---|---|\n507: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get`, `list`, `watch` | 读取 Sandbox 状态和注解 |\n508: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `delete` | 删除过期 Sandbox |\n509: \n510: ### 7.3 Resource Requirements\n511: \n512: | Resource | Request | Limit | Rationale |\n513: |---|---|---|---|\n514: | CPU | 50m | 200m | 控制器轻量，仅在事件触发时工作 |\n515: | Memory | 64Mi | 128Mi | controller-runtime informer cache 占用 |\n516: \n517: ### 7.4 Coexistence with LifecycleManager\n518: \n519: | Aspect | agentd | LifecycleManager |\n520: |---|---|---|\n521: | Trigger | K8s watch (event-driven) | Polling Redis Store (5min interval) |\n522: | Data Source | Sandbox CR annotations | Redis Store entries |\n523: | Cleanup Scope | Idle only (15min) | TTL + Idle + Orphan + Ghost |\n524: | Delete Idempotency | `IsNotFound` → success | `IsNotFound` → success |\n525: | Failure Mode | Falls back to LifecycleManager | Falls back to agentd |\n526: \n527: 两者互补运行，互不依赖，Delete 操作天然幂等。\n528: \n529: ## 8. Implementation Steps\n530: \n531: ### Phase 1: 常量定义\n532: \n533: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`，定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n534: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/const.go`，定义 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n535: \n536: ### Phase 2: Reconciler 实现\n537: \n538: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`\n539: - [ ] 实现 `Reconciler` 结构体（嵌入 `client.Client` + `*runtime.Scheme`）\n540: - [ ] 实现 `Reconcile` 方法（完整算法）\n541: - [ ] 实现 `SetupWithManager` 方法\n542: \n543: ### Phase 3: Binary Entry Point\n544: \n545: - [ ] 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n546: - [ ] Scheme 注册（core + `sandboxv1alpha1`）\n547: - [ ] Manager 构造（禁用 metrics/health probe）\n548: - [ ] Reconciler 注册 + Start\n549: \n550: ### Phase 4: 单元测试\n551: \n552: - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`\n553: - [ ] 实现所有测试用例（见 6.1 测试矩阵）\n554: - [ ] 验证 `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` 全部通过\n555: \n556: ### Phase 5: 代码质量门禁\n557: \n558: - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 无告警\n559: - [ ] `go mod tidy` 无变更\n560: - [ ] 验收标准对照检查（见 proposal.md 验收标准）\n561: \n562: ## 9. Future Changes\n563: \n564: - **可配置过期阈值**：当前固定 15 分钟，未来可从 ConfigMap 或 Sandbox annotation 读取自定义阈值\n565: - **Metrics 集成**：启用 metrics 服务，暴露 `agentd_sandboxes_cleaned_total`、`agentd_reconcile_duration_seconds` 等指标\n566: - **Leader Election**：多副本部署时启用 controller-runtime leader election，避免重复删除\n567: - **Grace Period**：删除前添加宽限期，允许 Sandbox 内进程完成清理\n568: - **Event Recording**：删除 Sandbox 时记录 Kubernetes Event，便于审计和调试\n569: - **Finalizer 支持**：在删除前执行自定义清理逻辑（如清理关联的 ConfigMap/Secret）\n\n(End of file - total 569 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n实现一个独立的 `agentd` 组件，作为基于 controller-runtime 的 Kubernetes 控制器，负责 watch `Sandbox` CR（`agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）并根据 `last-activity-time` 注解自动清理空闲沙箱。与 WorkloadManager 的 `LifecycleManager`（基于 Redis Store 轮询）形成双层清理保障，提供更可靠、低延迟的空闲检测能力。\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n```\ncmd/agentd/\n└── main.go              — Binary 入口：Scheme 注册、Manager 构造、启动\npkg/agentd/\n├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler 结构体 + Reconcile + SetupWithManager\n├── reconciler_test.go   — 单元测试（fake client）\n└── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout 常量\npkg/workloadmanager/\n└── const.go             — LastActivityAnnotationKey 常量（新增）\n```","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/design.md","time":{"start":1775846809067,"end":1775846809074}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846810425,"sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","part":{"id":"prt_d78b7de67001NLbWjh50Rc4mJ8","messageID":"msg_d78b7c4f50019W3bXKuS3X5eav","sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d050ade56178453789a2dea8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/agentd`, `cmd/agentd`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** S\n8: - **Base specs:** `idle-cleanup/spec.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: Reconciler watches Sandbox CR\n13: \n14: The system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API group `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`. The reconciler SHALL be triggered on Sandbox create and update events via `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Sandbox creation triggers reconcile\n17: \n18: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n19: - **WHEN** a new `Sandbox` object is created in the cluster\n20: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: Sandbox update triggers reconcile\n23: \n24: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n25: - **WHEN** an existing `Sandbox` object is updated (including annotation changes)\n26: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: Sandbox deletion triggers reconcile\n29: \n30: - **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n31: - **WHEN** a `Sandbox` object is deleted from the cluster\n32: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked and returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without error\n33: \n34: ### Requirement: Reconciler data structures\n35: \n36: The system SHALL define the following types in `pkg/agentd`:\n37: \n38: ```go\n39: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n40: \n41: type Reconciler struct {\n42:     client.Client\n43:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n44: }\n45: ```\n46: \n47: `SessionExpirationTimeout` SHALL be the fixed idle expiration threshold. The `Reconciler` struct SHALL embed `client.Client` for API server operations and hold a `*runtime.Scheme` for type registration.\n48: \n49: #### Scenario: SessionExpirationTimeout is 15 minutes\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** the `pkg/agentd` package is imported\n52: - **WHEN** `SessionExpirationTimeout` is read\n53: - **THEN** its value equals `15 * time.Minute`\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: Reconciler embeds client.Client\n56: \n57: - **GIVEN** a `Reconciler` instance is constructed\n58: - **WHEN** the instance is used\n59: - **THEN** it can call `Get`, `Delete`, and other `client.Client` methods directly\n60: \n61: ### Requirement: Get Sandbox and handle not found\n62: \n63: The `Reconcile` method SHALL retrieve the `Sandbox` object using `r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`. When the API server returns `NotFound`, the reconciler SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without error.\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Sandbox no longer exists\n66: \n67: - **GIVEN** a reconcile request for namespace `\"default\"`, name `\"sandbox-abc\"`\n68: - **WHEN** `r.Get` returns `errors.IsNotFound(err)`\n69: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: API server error on Get\n72: \n73: - **GIVEN** a reconcile request for a valid Sandbox\n74: - **WHEN** `r.Get` returns a non-NotFound error (e.g., connection refused)\n75: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry\n76: \n77: ### Requirement: Idle detection via annotation\n78: \n79: The system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the Sandbox metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` without delete action or requeue.\n80: \n81: The constant `LastActivityAnnotationKey` SHALL be defined in `pkg/workloadmanager` with value `\"last-activity-time\"`.\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Annotation is missing\n84: \n85: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with no `last-activity-time` annotation\n86: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n87: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` and the Sandbox is not deleted\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Annotation is empty string\n90: \n91: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time: \"\"`\n92: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n93: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` and the Sandbox is not deleted\n94: \n95: ### Requirement: Timestamp parsing\n96: \n97: When the `last-activity-time` annotation is non-empty, the system SHALL parse it with `time.RFC3339`. On parse error, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err)`.\n98: \n99: #### Scenario: Valid RFC3339 timestamp\n100: \n101: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"2026-04-10T10:00:00Z\"`\n102: - **WHEN** `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, ...)` is called\n103: - **THEN** parsing succeeds and returns the corresponding `time.Time` value\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: Invalid timestamp format\n106: \n107: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"not-a-timestamp\"`\n108: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n109: - **THEN** the reconciler returns `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)` where `err` is the parse error\n110: \n111: #### Scenario: Partial RFC3339 timestamp\n112: \n113: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is `\"2026-04-10\"`\n114: - **WHEN** `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, ...)` is called\n115: - **THEN** parsing fails and reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`\n116: \n117: ### Requirement: Expiration threshold and delete\n118: \n119: The system SHALL compute `expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`. When `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`, the system SHALL call `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)` to remove the Sandbox resource.\n120: \n121: #### Scenario: Sandbox idle beyond 15 minutes\n122: \n123: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:16:00Z`\n124: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n125: - **THEN** `expirationTime` is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`, `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is true, and `r.Delete` is called\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Sandbox not yet expired\n128: \n129: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:05:00Z`\n130: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n131: - **THEN** `expirationTime` is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`, `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is false, and no delete occurs\n132: \n133: #### Scenario: Exactly at expiration boundary\n134: \n135: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z` and current time is `2026-04-10T10:15:00Z`\n136: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n137: - **THEN** `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` is false (equal, not after), and result is `RequeueAfter` with a small positive duration or zero\n138: \n139: ### Requirement: Requeue until expiration\n140: \n141: When the Sandbox is not yet expired, the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)` to schedule the next reconciliation at the exact expiration time.\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: RequeueAfter is positive duration\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** `expirationTime` is 10 minutes in the future\n146: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n147: - **THEN** the result is `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}` and `Requeue` is false\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: RequeueAfter approaches zero near expiration\n150: \n151: - **GIVEN** `expirationTime` is 1 second in the future\n152: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n153: - **THEN** the result is `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: ~1s}`\n154: \n155: ### Requirement: Delete idempotency\n156: \n157: When `r.Delete` returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL treat it as success and return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`. Other delete errors SHALL be returned as `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry.\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: Sandbox already deleted by another controller\n160: \n161: - **GIVEN** the LifecycleManager deleted the Sandbox between reconcile Get and Delete\n162: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` returns `errors.IsNotFound(err)`\n163: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: Delete fails with transient error\n166: \n167: - **GIVEN** the API server returns a connection error on Delete\n168: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` is called\n169: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, err)` to trigger retry\n170: \n171: ### Requirement: Successful delete result\n172: \n173: When `r.Delete` succeeds (returns nil error), the system SHALL return `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`.\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: Delete succeeds\n176: \n177: - **GIVEN** the Sandbox exists and is expired\n178: - **WHEN** `r.Delete` returns nil\n179: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n180: \n181: ### Requirement: SetupWithManager\n182: \n183: The system SHALL provide a `SetupWithManager` method on `Reconciler` that registers the controller with the manager:\n184: \n185: ```go\n186: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n187:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n188:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n189:         Complete(r)\n190: }\n191: ```\n192: \n193: #### Scenario: Controller is registered\n194: \n195: - **GIVEN** a valid `ctrl.Manager`\n196: - **WHEN** `r.SetupWithManager(mgr)` is called\n197: - **THEN** the function returns `nil` and the controller is registered to watch Sandbox resources\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Scheme registration\n200: \n201: The `cmd/agentd/main.go` SHALL construct a scheme containing core Kubernetes types and `sandboxv1alpha1` from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`:\n202: \n203: ```go\n204: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n205: \n206: func init() {\n207:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n208:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n209: }\n210: ```\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: Scheme contains core and Sandbox types\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** the `init` function has run\n215: - **WHEN** `schemeBuilder` is inspected\n216: - **THEN** it recognizes both core `v1.Pod` and `sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox` types\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Manager configuration\n219: \n220: The binary SHALL construct a controller-runtime Manager with the following options:\n221: \n222: ```go\n223: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n224:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n225:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n226:     HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n227: })\n228: ```\n229: \n230: Metrics server SHALL be disabled (`BindAddress: \"0\"`). Health probe server SHALL be disabled (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`).\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Manager starts without metrics or health endpoints\n233: \n234: - **GIVEN** a valid kubeconfig is available\n235: - **WHEN** `ctrl.NewManager` is called with the specified options\n236: - **THEN** no metrics or health probe HTTP servers are started\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: Invalid kubeconfig fails fast\n239: \n240: - **GIVEN** no valid kubeconfig is available\n241: - **WHEN** `ctrl.GetConfigOrDie()` is called\n242: - **THEN** the process exits with a non-zero status\n243: \n244: ### Requirement: Binary entry point — Controller registration and startup\n245: \n246: The binary SHALL register the reconciler and start the manager:\n247: \n248: ```go\n249: if err := (&agentd.Reconciler{\n250:     Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n251:     Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n252: }).SetupWithManager(mgr); err != nil {\n253:     // exit with error\n254: }\n255: \n256: if err := mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()); err != nil {\n257:     // exit with error\n258: }\n259: ```\n260: \n261: #### Scenario: Signal-driven graceful shutdown\n262: \n263: - **GIVEN** the manager is running\n264: - **WHEN** SIGTERM or SIGINT is received\n265: - **THEN** `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` triggers graceful shutdown and `mgr.Start` returns\n266: \n267: ### Requirement: Package layout\n268: \n269: The system SHALL organize code as follows:\n270: \n271: ```\n272: cmd/agentd/\n273: └── main.go              — Binary entry point\n274: pkg/agentd/\n275: ├── reconciler.go        — Reconciler struct, Reconcile, SetupWithManager\n276: ├── reconciler_test.go   — Unit tests\n277: └── const.go             — SessionExpirationTimeout constant\n278: ```\n279: \n280: #### Scenario: Package compiles\n281: \n282: - **GIVEN** all files are in place\n283: - **WHEN** `go build ./cmd/agentd/` is run\n284: - **THEN** the build succeeds and produces an `agentd` binary\n285: \n286: #### Scenario: Package tests pass\n287: \n288: - **GIVEN** all test cases are implemented\n289: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` is run\n290: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n291: \n292: ### Requirement: Reconcile algorithm completeness\n293: \n294: The `Reconcile` method SHALL implement the following algorithm exactly:\n295: \n296: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`\n297: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n298: 3. If other get error → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n299: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`\n300: 5. If `!exists || lastActivityStr == \"\"` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n301: 6. `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n302: 7. If parse error → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n303: 8. `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n304: 9. If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n305:    - `err := r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`\n306:    - If err and not `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n307:    - `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n308: 10. Else → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n309: \n310: #### Scenario: Full happy path — expired sandbox deleted\n311: \n312: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time` set to 20 minutes ago\n313: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n314: - **THEN** steps 1-9 execute, `Delete` is called, and `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` is returned\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: Full happy path — not yet expired requeues\n317: \n318: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox with `last-activity-time` set to 5 minutes ago\n319: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n320: - **THEN** steps 1-8 and 10 execute, returning `RequeueAfter: ~10m`\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: Missing annotation short-circuits\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** a Sandbox without `last-activity-time`\n325: - **WHEN** `Reconcile` is called\n326: - **THEN** steps 1-5 execute, returning `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)` at step 5\n327: \n328: ### Requirement: Code quality gates\n329: \n330: The codebase SHALL pass the following checks after implementation:\n331: \n332: - `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` produces no warnings\n333: - `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` passes all tests\n334: - `go mod tidy` results in no changes\n335: \n336: #### Scenario: go vet clean\n337: \n338: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n339: - **WHEN** `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` is run\n340: - **THEN** no warnings or errors are reported\n341: \n342: #### Scenario: All tests pass\n343: \n344: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n345: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` is run\n346: - **THEN** all tests pass with exit code 0\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: No unused dependencies\n349: \n350: - **GIVEN** AR-018 is implemented\n351: - **WHEN** `go mod tidy` is run\n352: - **THEN** `go.mod` and `go.sum` are unchanged\n\n(End of file - total 352 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/agentd`, `cmd/agentd`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `idle-cleanup/spec.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Reconciler watches Sandbox CR\n\nThe system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API group `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`. The reconciler SHALL be triggered on Sandbox create and update events via `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`.\n\n#### Scenario: Sandbox creation triggers reconcile\n\n- **GIVEN** the agentd manager is running\n- **WHEN** a new `Sandbox` object is created in the cluster\n- **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object's namespace and name","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775846810416,"end":1775846810423}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846811875,"sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","part":{"id":"prt_d78b7e3bd001PGq0GyCcAlwdCt","messageID":"msg_d78b7c4f50019W3bXKuS3X5eav","sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_e47c2c6d400d48838907dd3e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n13: - [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n14: \n15: **Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n20: \n21: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/picod/auth.go`\n22: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `AuthManager` 结构体，字段：`publicKey *rsa.PublicKey`，`mutex sync.RWMutex`\n23: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `newAuthManager() *AuthManager` 私有构造函数，返回空的 `AuthManager` 实例\n24: - [ ] 2.4 实现 `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error` 方法：\n25:   - 读取环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`，为空返回 `\"environment variable %s is not set\"`\n26:   - PEM 解码，失败返回 `\"failed to decode PEM block\"`\n27:   - `x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey` 解析，失败返回 `\"failed to parse public key: %w\"`\n28:   - 类型断言为 `*rsa.PublicKey`，非 RSA 返回 `\"public key is not RSA\"`\n29:   - 获取写锁，存储公钥，释放锁\n30: - [ ] 2.5 实现 `checkFatal(err error)` 辅助函数：`err != nil` 时调用 `klog.Fatalf(\"failed to load public key: %v\", err)`\n31: - [ ] 2.6 创建 `pkg/picod/auth_test.go`\n32: - [ ] 2.7 实现测试辅助函数：`generateTestPrivateKey(t) *rsa.PrivateKey`（2048-bit RSA）、`generateTestPublicKey(t) string`（PEM 编码公钥）\n33: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_ValidKey`：设置有效 RSA 公钥 → `err == nil`，`publicKey != nil`\n34: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_MissingEnv`：环境变量未设置 → `err != nil`，包含 \"not set\"\n35: - [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_InvalidPEM`：环境变量为 `\"not-a-pem-block\"` → `err != nil`，包含 \"failed to decode PEM block\"\n36: - [ ] 2.11 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_NonRSAKey`：环境变量包含非 RSA 公钥（EC 密钥） → `err != nil`，包含 \"public key is not RSA\"\n37: \n38: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthManager structure and public key loading 全部 4 个场景\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T3. 实现 AuthMiddleware JWT 验证中间件\n43: \n44: - [ ] 3.1 在 `pkg/picod/auth.go` 中实现 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法\n45: - [ ] 3.2 提取 `Authorization` 请求头，缺失时返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n46: - [ ] 3.3 按空格分割验证 `Bearer <token>` 格式，格式错误返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid Authorization header format\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\"}`\n47: - [ ] 3.4 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证 JWT，KeyFunc 中：\n48:   - 检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`，否则返回 `\"unexpected signing method: %v\"`\n49:   - 获取读锁，返回 `am.publicKey`\n50:   - 选项：`jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`、`jwt.WithIssuedAt()`、`jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)`\n51: - [ ] 3.5 验证失败（`err != nil || !token.Valid`）返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"<具体错误>\"}`\n52: - [ ] 3.6 验证通过：`c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)`，然后 `c.Next()`\n53: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MissingAuthHeader`：无 Authorization 头 → 401\n54: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MalformedAuthHeader`：`Authorization: \"InvalidFormat\"` → 401\n55: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken`：有效 RS256 JWT（exp 未来，iat 过去） → 200\n56: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ExpiredToken`：exp 为 5 分钟前 → 401\n57: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_NonRSASigningMethod`：HS256 签名的 JWT → 401\n58: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MaxBodySize`：验证通过后 Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装\n59: \n60: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthMiddleware JWT validation 全部 7 个场景\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## T4. Server 集成 — 路由注册与认证中间件应用\n65: \n66: - [ ] 4.1 在 `pkg/picod/server.go` 的 `Server` 结构体中增加 `authManager *AuthManager` 字段\n67: - [ ] 4.2 在 `NewServer(config)` 中：\n68:   - 调用 `newAuthManager()` 创建实例\n69:   - 调用 `authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`，失败则 `checkFatal(err)` 终止进程\n70:   - 将 `authManager` 存入 Server 结构体\n71: - [ ] 4.3 在 `registerRoutes()` 中：\n72:   - 创建 `/api` 路由组：`api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")`\n73:   - 应用中间件：`api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())`\n74:   - 注册业务端点到 `/api` 组：`POST /execute`、`POST /files`、`GET /files`、`GET /files/*path`\n75:   - `/health` 端点保持在路由组外：`s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)`\n76: - [ ] 4.4 测试 `TestServer_HealthEndpointPublic`：`GET /health` 无 Authorization 头 → 200\n77: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesRequireAuth`：`POST /api/execute` 无 Authorization 头 → 401\n78: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesAcceptValidJWT`：`POST /api/execute` 带有效 JWT → 200\n79: \n80: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Route protection with AuthMiddleware 全部 3 个场景\n81: \n82: ---\n83: \n84: ## T5. 时钟容差（Leeway）验证\n85: \n86: - [ ] 5.1 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway`：JWT 的 exp 设为 30 秒前，iat 设为 30 秒前 → 200（在 1 分钟 leeway 窗口内被接受）\n87: \n88: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway -v` 通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Scenario: Clock leeway tolerates minor skew\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## T6. 线程安全验证\n93: \n94: - [ ] 6.1 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReads`：多个 goroutine 同时调用 AuthMiddleware → 无死锁\n95: - [ ] 6.2 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReadWrite`：一个 goroutine 调用 LoadPublicKeyFromEnv 的同时，其他 goroutine 调用 AuthMiddleware → 无数据竞争\n96: \n97: **Verification:** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` 无数据竞争警告；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Thread-safe public key access\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## T7. 代码质量门禁\n102: \n103: - [ ] 7.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n104: - [ ] 7.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` 确认全部测试通过\n105: - [ ] 7.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无数据竞争\n106: - [ ] 7.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无警告\n107: - [ ] 7.5 确认代码中无 `log.Printf` 使用（仅使用 `klog`）\n108: - [ ] 7.6 确认错误响应中不泄露 JWT token 或密钥材料\n109: \n110: **Verification:** 所有门禁命令 exit code 0；无敏感数据出现在日志或错误响应中\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## Task Dependencies\n115: \n116: ```\n117: T1\n118: │\n119: T2 ── T3 ── T4\n120:       │     │\n121:       T5    T6\n122:       │     │\n123:       └─────┴── T7\n124: ```\n125: \n126: **Parallel execution:**\n127: - T2 和 T3 可并行开发（T2 定义结构体和方法签名后，T3 即可开始实现中间件逻辑）\n128: - T5（leeway 测试）可与 T4 并行\n129: - T6（并发测试）需 T2 和 T3 完成后开始\n130: - T7 为最终门禁，需所有前置任务完成\n131: \n132: ---\n133: \n134: ## Acceptance Criteria\n135: \n136: | # | Criterion | Command |\n137: |---|-----------|---------|\n138: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/picod/...` |\n139: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` |\n140: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` |\n141: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` |\n142: | AC5 | AuthManager 公钥加载覆盖 4 个场景（有效/缺失/无效PEM/非RSA） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv -v` |\n143: | AC6 | AuthMiddleware 覆盖 7 个场景（缺失header/格式错误/有效/过期/非RSA/MaxBody/leeway） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` |\n144: | AC7 | Server 路由保护验证（/health 公开，/api 需认证） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` |\n145: | AC8 | 线程安全验证（并发读、并发读写无竞争） | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` |\n146: | AC9 | 无 `log.Printf` 使用 | `grep -r 'log\\.Printf' pkg/picod/` 无输出 |\n147: | AC10 | 错误响应不泄露敏感信息 | 审查 auth.go 中所有 401 响应体 |\n\n(End of file - total 147 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/picod\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n- [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n- [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775846811865,"end":1775846811872}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846813209,"sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","part":{"id":"prt_d78b7e958001XaPRV19LWxtM64","messageID":"msg_d78b7c4f50019W3bXKuS3X5eav","sessionID":"ses_2874b3e7cffeHcaG0cXjiTR7WF","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_728a6eb1ee444912956c3cf7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-016/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-016/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-016/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-016/design.md`, `design.md`, `delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 创建 files/ 子包脚手架、类型和常量\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/` 目录\n12: - [ ] 1.2 创建 `pkg/picod/files/types.go`\n13: - [ ] 1.3 定义 `FileManager` 接口，包含 12 个方法：`ReadFile`, `WriteFile`, `StatFile`, `ListFiles`, `UploadFile`, `UploadFileChunked`, `DownloadFile`, `DeleteFile`, `MoveFile`, `MkDir`, `SearchFiles`, `Chmod`\n14: - [ ] 1.4 定义 `fileManager` 实现结构体，字段：`workspaceDir string`, `resolvedWorkspace string`, `maxChunkSize int64`, `maxBatchSize int`, `maxSearchResults int`, `maxSearchDepth int`, `tempDir string`\n15: - [ ] 1.5 定义请求/响应结构体：`ReadFileRequest`, `ReadFileResponse`, `WriteFileRequest`, `WriteFileResponse`, `StatFileResponse`, `ListFilesResponse`, `FileEntry`, `UploadFileRequest`, `ChunkedUploadRequest`, `DownloadFileRequest`, `DownloadFileResponse`, `DeleteFileRequest`, `DeleteFileResponse`, `DeleteFailure`, `MoveFileRequest`, `MoveFileResponse`, `MkDirRequest`, `MkDirResponse`, `SearchFilesRequest`, `SearchFilesResponse`, `ChmodRequest`, `ChmodResponse`（所有 JSON 标签与 design.md §2.3 一致）\n16: - [ ] 1.6 定义常量：`DefaultMaxChunkSize = 32 << 20`（33554432），`DefaultMaxBatchSize = 100`，`DefaultMaxSearchResults = 100`，`DefaultMaxSearchDepth = 50`，`DefaultDirMode = \"0755\"`，`DefaultFileMode = \"0644\"`，`MaxFileMode = 0777`，`ChunkExt = \".chunk\"`\n17: - [ ] 1.7 定义哨兵错误：`ErrPathTraversal`, `ErrFileNotFound`, `ErrDirectoryNotFound`, `ErrIsDirectory`, `ErrNotADirectory`, `ErrInvalidBase64`, `ErrInvalidMode`, `ErrModeOutOfRange`, `ErrChunkTooLarge`, `ErrRangeNotSatisfiable`, `ErrBatchSizeExceeded`, `ErrDirectoryNotEmpty`, `ErrPathAlreadyExists`, `ErrWorkspaceNotInitialized`\n18: - [ ] 1.8 定义 `FileConfig` 结构体（用于 config.go 扩展），字段：`MaxChunkSize int64`, `MaxBatchSize int`, `MaxSearchResults int`, `MaxSearchDepth int`\n19: - [ ] 1.9 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n20: \n21: **Verification:** 所有结构体 JSON 标签与 design.md §2.3 一致；常量值正确；错误变量均有明确语义；编译零错误\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## T2. 迁移 sanitizePath 至 files/ 子包\n26: \n27: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/sanitize.go`\n28: - [ ] 2.2 将 `sanitizePath` 作为 `fileManager` 的方法实现：\n29:   - `resolvedWorkspace` 为空返回 `ErrWorkspaceNotInitialized`\n30:   - `filepath.Clean(p)` 规范化路径\n31:   - 绝对路径去除前导 `os.PathSeparator`\n32:   - `fullPathCandidate := filepath.Clean(filepath.Join(fm.resolvedWorkspace, cleanPath))`\n33:   - `filepath.Rel` 验证，失败返回 `ErrPathTraversal`\n34:   - 若 `relPath` 以 `\"..\" + separator` 开头或等于 `\"..\"`，返回 `ErrPathTraversal`\n35:   - `filepath.EvalSymlinks(fullPathCandidate)` 解析符号链接：\n36:     - 成功：再次 `filepath.Rel` 验证，通过则返回解析后路径，否则返回 `ErrPathTraversal`\n37:     - 失败（路径不存在）：返回已验证的 `fullPathCandidate`\n38: - [ ] 2.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/sanitize_test.go`\n39: - [ ] 2.4 测试 `TestSanitizePath_NormalPath`：`\"hello.txt\"` → workspace/hello.txt\n40: - [ ] 2.5 测试 `TestSanitizePath_Subdirectory`：`\"src/main.go\"` → workspace/src/main.go\n41: - [ ] 2.6 测试 `TestSanitizePath_AbsolutePath`：`\"/etc/passwd\"` → workspace/etc/passwd（前导 `/` 被去除）\n42: - [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestSanitizePath_ParentTraversal`：`\"../../etc/passwd\"` → `ErrPathTraversal`\n43: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestSanitizePath_SymlinkEscape`：symlink 指向 workspace 外 → `ErrPathTraversal`\n44: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestSanitizePath_EmptyPath`：`\"\"` → workspace 根目录\n45: - [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestSanitizePath_UninitializedWorkspace`：`resolvedWorkspace` 为空 → `ErrWorkspaceNotInitialized`\n46: \n47: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestSanitizePath -v` 全部通过；覆盖 design.md §3.14 路径安全校验全部场景\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## T3. 实现 FileManager 构造函数\n52: \n53: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/manager.go`\n54: - [ ] 3.2 实现 `NewFileManager(workspaceDir string, cfg FileConfig) (FileManager, error)` 构造函数：\n55:   - `filepath.Abs(workspaceDir)` 解析绝对路径\n56:   - `filepath.EvalSymlinks(resolved)` 解析符号链接，失败则 `filepath.Clean` 回退\n57:   - 配置默认值填充：`MaxChunkSize <= 0` → `DefaultMaxChunkSize`，`MaxBatchSize <= 0` → `DefaultMaxBatchSize`，`MaxSearchResults <= 0` → `DefaultMaxSearchResults`，`MaxSearchDepth <= 0` → `DefaultMaxSearchDepth`\n58:   - 创建临时目录 `filepath.Join(os.TempDir(), \"picod-chunks\")`，`os.MkdirAll(tempDir, 0700)`\n59:   - 返回 `&fileManager{...}` 实例\n60: - [ ] 3.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/manager_test.go`\n61: - [ ] 3.4 测试 `TestNewFileManager_Defaults`：零值配置 → 默认 limits 被应用\n62: - [ ] 3.5 测试 `TestNewFileManager_CustomConfig`：自定义配置 → limits 被正确设置\n63: - [ ] 3.6 测试 `TestNewFileManager_InvalidWorkspace`：非法 workspace 路径 → 错误处理\n64: \n65: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestNewFileManager -v` 全部通过\n66: \n67: ---\n68: \n69: ## T4. 实现 ReadFile（offset/limit 片段读取）\n70: \n71: - [ ] 4.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/read.go`\n72: - [ ] 4.2 实现 `ReadFile(ctx context.Context, req *ReadFileRequest) (*ReadFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n73:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n74:   - `os.Stat(safePath)` 检查文件存在性，不存在返回 `ErrFileNotFound`\n75:   - 路径为目录返回 `ErrIsDirectory`\n76:   - `os.Open(safePath)` 打开文件，defer Close\n77:   - `offset < 0` 时视为 0\n78:   - `f.Seek(offset, io.SeekStart)` 定位\n79:   - `limit < 0` 时 `io.ReadAll(f)` 读到末尾；否则 `make([]byte, req.Limit)` + `f.Read(data)`\n80:   - Base64 编码内容，返回 `ReadFileResponse{Content, TotalSize, ReadBytes}`\n81: - [ ] 4.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/read_test.go`\n82: - [ ] 4.4 测试 `TestReadFile_EntireFile`：读取完整文件 → Base64 内容、total_size、read_bytes 正确\n83: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestReadFile_WithOffset`：offset=7 → 从偏移处读取\n84: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestReadFile_WithOffsetAndLimit`：offset=7, limit=5 → 读取 5 字节\n85: - [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestReadFile_OffsetExceedsSize`：offset > 文件大小 → 空内容，read_bytes=0\n86: - [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestReadFile_LimitExceedsRemaining`：limit > 剩余字节 → 读到 EOF\n87: - [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestReadFile_NegativeOffset`：offset=-1 → 视为 0\n88: - [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestReadFile_Directory`：路径为目录 → `ErrIsDirectory`\n89: - [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestReadFile_NotFound`：路径不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n90: - [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestReadFile_PathTraversal`：`\"../../etc/passwd\"` → `ErrPathTraversal`\n91: \n92: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestReadFile -v` 全部通过\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: ## T5. 实现 WriteFile（offset/append/overwrite 模式）\n97: \n98: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/write.go`\n99: - [ ] 5.2 实现 `WriteFile(ctx context.Context, req *WriteFileRequest) (*WriteFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n100:   - `base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString(req.Content)` 解码，失败返回 `ErrInvalidBase64`\n101:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n102:   - 路径为已存在目录返回 `ErrIsDirectory`\n103:   - `req.CreateParent` 为 true 时 `os.MkdirAll(filepath.Dir(safePath), 0755)`\n104:   - 模式选择：`mode=\"append\"` → `O_CREATE|O_WRONLY|O_APPEND`；`mode=\"overwrite\"` 且 `offset>0` → `O_CREATE|O_WRONLY`；默认 → `O_CREATE|O_WRONLY|O_TRUNC`\n105:   - `offset > 0` 且非 append 模式时 `f.Seek(req.Offset, io.SeekStart)`\n106:   - `f.Write(data)` 写入，返回 `WriteFileResponse{Path, Size, BytesWritten}`\n107: - [ ] 5.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/write_test.go`\n108: - [ ] 5.4 测试 `TestWriteFile_Overwrite`：覆盖模式替换文件内容\n109: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestWriteFile_Append`：追加模式在末尾添加\n110: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestWriteFile_AtOffset`：在指定偏移处写入，不截断后续内容\n111: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestWriteFile_CreateParent`：`create_parent=true` → 父目录自动创建\n112: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestWriteFile_NoCreateParent`：`create_parent=false`，父目录缺失 → 错误\n113: - [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestWriteFile_InvalidBase64`：无效 Base64 → `ErrInvalidBase64`\n114: - [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestWriteFile_ToDirectory`：路径为目录 → `ErrIsDirectory`\n115: \n116: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestWriteFile -v` 全部通过\n117: \n118: ---\n119: \n120: ## T6. 实现 StatFile（文件元数据查询）\n121: \n122: - [ ] 6.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/stat.go`\n123: - [ ] 6.2 实现 `StatFile(ctx context.Context, path string) (*StatFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n124:   - `sanitizePath(path)` 校验路径\n125:   - `os.Lstat(safePath)` 获取元数据（使用 Lstat 以检测符号链接）\n126:   - 不存在返回 `ErrFileNotFound`\n127:   - 返回 `StatFileResponse{Name, Size, Mode(八进制字符串), ModTime, IsDir, IsSymlink}`\n128: - [ ] 6.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/stat_test.go`\n129: - [ ] 6.4 测试 `TestStatFile_RegularFile`：文件元数据正确返回\n130: - [ ] 6.5 测试 `TestStatFile_Directory`：`is_dir: true`\n131: - [ ] 6.6 测试 `TestStatFile_Symlink`：`is_symlink: true`\n132: - [ ] 6.7 测试 `TestStatFile_NotFound`：路径不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n133: - [ ] 6.8 测试 `TestStatFile_PathTraversal`：穿越路径 → `ErrPathTraversal`\n134: \n135: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestStatFile -v` 全部通过\n136: \n137: ---\n138: \n139: ## T7. 迁移 ListFiles（目录列表）\n140: \n141: - [ ] 7.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/list.go`\n142: - [ ] 7.2 实现 `ListFiles(ctx context.Context, path string) (*ListFilesResponse, error)` 方法：\n143:   - `sanitizePath(path)` 校验路径\n144:   - `os.ReadDir(safePath)` 读取目录，`os.IsNotExist` 返回 `ErrFileNotFound`\n145:   - 路径不是目录返回 `ErrNotADirectory`\n146:   - 遍历 entries，`entry.Info()` 失败则跳过\n147:   - 构建 `[]FileEntry` 列表，返回 `ListFilesResponse{Files}`\n148: - [ ] 7.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/list_test.go`\n149: - [ ] 7.4 测试 `TestListFiles_DirectoryContents`：返回目录文件条目列表\n150: - [ ] 7.5 测试 `TestListFiles_MissingPath`：空路径 → 错误\n151: - [ ] 7.6 测试 `TestListFiles_NotFound`：目录不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n152: - [ ] 7.7 测试 `TestListFiles_NotDirectory`：路径不是目录 → `ErrNotADirectory`\n153: \n154: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestListFiles -v` 全部通过；行为与 AR-015 原有 ListFilesHandler 一致\n155: \n156: ---\n157: \n158: ## T8. 迁移 UploadFile（增加分块支持）\n159: \n160: - [ ] 8.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/upload.go`\n161: - [ ] 8.2 实现 `UploadFile(ctx context.Context, req *UploadFileRequest) (*FileInfo, error)` 方法（JSON Base64 模式）：\n162:   - `base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString(req.Content)` 解码\n163:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n164:   - `os.MkdirAll(filepath.Dir(safePath), 0755)` 创建父目录\n165:   - `os.WriteFile(safePath, data, parseFileMode(req.Mode))` 写入\n166:   - 返回 `FileInfo{Path, Size, Mode, Modified}`\n167: - [ ] 8.3 实现 `UploadFileChunked(ctx context.Context, req *ChunkedUploadRequest) (*FileInfo, error)` 方法：\n168:   - 解码 Base64，校验 chunk 大小 ≤ `maxChunkSize`，超限返回 `ErrChunkTooLarge`\n169:   - 写入临时文件 `<tempDir>/<basename>.chunk.<index>`\n170:   - 最后一块（`ChunkIndex == ChunkTotal-1`）触发 `mergeChunks` 合并\n171: - [ ] 8.4 实现 `mergeChunks(finalPath, relPath string, totalChunks int, mode os.FileMode) (*FileInfo, error)` 方法：\n172:   - 按顺序读取所有 `.chunk.<i>` 文件，写入最终文件\n173:   - `defer cleanupChunks(relPath, totalChunks)` 清理临时文件\n174:   - 返回合并后的 `FileInfo`\n175: - [ ] 8.5 实现 `cleanupChunks(relPath string, totalChunks int)` 方法：删除所有临时 chunk 文件\n176: - [ ] 8.6 实现 `parseFileMode(modeStr string) os.FileMode` 辅助函数（从 files.go 迁移）\n177: - [ ] 8.7 创建 `pkg/picod/files/upload_test.go`\n178: - [ ] 8.8 测试 `TestUpload_Multipart`：multipart 表单上传成功\n179: - [ ] 8.9 测试 `TestUpload_JSONBase64`：JSON Base64 上传成功\n180: - [ ] 8.10 测试 `TestUpload_ChunkedSingle`：单块上传（无分块头）→ 直接写入\n181: - [ ] 8.11 测试 `TestUpload_ChunkedMulti`：3 块上传 → 合并正确\n182: - [ ] 8.12 测试 `TestUpload_ChunkedOutOfOrder`：块 2,0,1 到达 → 按 0,1,2 顺序组装\n183: - [ ] 8.13 测试 `TestUpload_ChunkExceedsMax`：块大小 > MaxChunkSize → `ErrChunkTooLarge`\n184: - [ ] 8.14 测试 `TestUpload_ChunkCleanup`：合并后无 `.chunk.*` 临时文件残留\n185: \n186: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestUpload -v` 全部通过；行为与 AR-015 原有 UploadFileHandler 一致且增加分块支持\n187: \n188: ---\n189: \n190: ## T9. 迁移 DownloadFile（增加 Range 支持）\n191: \n192: - [ ] 9.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/download.go`\n193: - [ ] 9.2 实现 `DownloadFile(ctx context.Context, req *DownloadFileRequest) (*DownloadFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n194:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n195:   - `os.Stat(safePath)` 检查文件，不存在返回 `ErrFileNotFound`，目录返回 `ErrIsDirectory`\n196:   - 若 `req.Range` 非空，调用 `handleRangeRequest` 处理分块\n197:   - 否则读取完整文件，检测 `Content-Type`（`mime.TypeByExtension` 或 `application/octet-stream`）\n198:   - 返回 `DownloadFileResponse{Content, ContentType, ContentLength, StatusCode: 200}`\n199: - [ ] 9.3 实现 `handleRangeRequest(f *os.File, rangeHeader string, totalSize int64, path string) (*DownloadFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n200:   - `parseRange(rangeHeader, totalSize)` 解析范围\n201:   - `start >= totalSize` 返回 `ErrRangeNotSatisfiable`\n202:   - `end >= totalSize` 时截断为 `totalSize - 1`\n203:   - Seek 到 start，读取 `length = end - start + 1` 字节\n204:   - 返回 `DownloadFileResponse{StatusCode: 206, ContentRange: \"bytes start-end/total\"}`\n205: - [ ] 9.4 实现 `parseRange(rangeHeader string, totalSize int64) (int64, int64, error)` 辅助函数：\n206:   - 解析 `bytes=start-end` 格式\n207:   - 支持 `bytes=start-`（读到末尾）\n208:   - 校验 `start <= end`\n209: - [ ] 9.5 创建 `pkg/picod/files/download_test.go`\n210: - [ ] 9.6 测试 `TestDownload_FullFile`：无 Range 头 → HTTP 200，完整内容\n211: - [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestDownload_RangePartial`：`Range: bytes=0-499` → HTTP 206，Content-Range 头\n212: - [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestDownload_RangeToEOF`：`Range: bytes=500-` → 从 500 到末尾\n213: - [ ] 9.9 测试 `TestDownload_RangeBeyondSize`：`Range: bytes=200-300` 在 100 字节文件上 → `ErrRangeNotSatisfiable`\n214: - [ ] 9.10 测试 `TestDownload_Directory`：路径为目录 → `ErrIsDirectory`\n215: - [ ] 9.11 测试 `TestDownload_NotFound`：路径不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n216: \n217: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestDownload -v` 全部通过；行为与 AR-015 原有 DownloadFileHandler 一致且增加 Range 支持\n218: \n219: ---\n220: \n221: ## T10. 实现 DeleteFile（单文件 + 批量删除）\n222: \n223: - [ ] 10.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/delete.go`\n224: - [ ] 10.2 实现 `DeleteFile(ctx context.Context, req *DeleteFileRequest) (*DeleteFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n225:   - 单 `Path` 非空：删除单个文件/空目录\n226:   - `Paths` 非空：批量删除，数量 > `maxBatchSize` 返回 `ErrBatchSizeExceeded`\n227:   - 使用 `os.Remove`（非 `os.RemoveAll`）— 目录必须为空\n228:   - 批量模式：继续处理失败项，分别记录 `Deleted` 和 `Failed` 列表\n229:   - 每个路径均需通过 `sanitizePath` 校验\n230: - [ ] 10.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/delete_test.go`\n231: - [ ] 10.4 测试 `TestDelete_SingleFile`：删除单个文件成功\n232: - [ ] 10.5 测试 `TestDelete_SingleNotFound`：文件不存在 → 错误\n233: - [ ] 10.6 测试 `TestDelete_BatchAllSuccess`：多个文件全部删除\n234: - [ ] 10.7 测试 `TestDelete_BatchPartialFailure`：部分成功部分失败 → 分别报告\n235: - [ ] 10.8 测试 `TestDelete_BatchExceedsMax`：超过 MaxBatchSize → `ErrBatchSizeExceeded`\n236: - [ ] 10.9 测试 `TestDelete_NonEmptyDirectory`：非空目录 → 错误\n237: - [ ] 10.10 测试 `TestDelete_EmptyDirectory`：空目录删除成功\n238: \n239: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestDelete -v` 全部通过\n240: \n241: ---\n242: \n243: ## T11. 实现 MoveFile（文件移动/重命名）\n244: \n245: - [ ] 11.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/move.go`\n246: - [ ] 11.2 实现 `MoveFile(ctx context.Context, req *MoveFileRequest) (*MoveFileResponse, error)` 方法：\n247:   - 对 `Source` 和 `Destination` 分别调用 `sanitizePath`\n248:   - 源路径不存在返回 `ErrFileNotFound`\n249:   - 目标父目录不存在返回错误\n250:   - 目标路径逃逸 workspace 返回 `ErrPathTraversal`\n251:   - `os.Rename(src, dst)` 执行移动\n252:   - 返回 `MoveFileResponse{Source, Destination}`\n253: - [ ] 11.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/move_test.go`\n254: - [ ] 11.4 测试 `TestMove_RenameFile`：同目录下重命名成功\n255: - [ ] 11.5 测试 `TestMove_MoveToSubdirectory`：移动到已存在的子目录\n256: - [ ] 11.6 测试 `TestMove_SourceNotFound`：源文件不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n257: - [ ] 11.7 测试 `TestMove_DestParentNotFound`：目标父目录不存在 → 错误\n258: - [ ] 11.8 测试 `TestMove_EscapeWorkspace`：目标路径逃逸 workspace → `ErrPathTraversal`\n259: \n260: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestMove -v` 全部通过\n261: \n262: ---\n263: \n264: ## T12. 实现 MkDir（递归创建目录）\n265: \n266: - [ ] 12.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/mkdir.go`\n267: - [ ] 12.2 实现 `MkDir(ctx context.Context, req *MkDirRequest) (*MkDirResponse, error)` 方法：\n268:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n269:   - 路径已存在且为文件返回 `ErrPathAlreadyExists`\n270:   - 路径已存在且为目录 → `created: false`，无错误\n271:   - 解析 mode（默认 `0755`）\n272:   - `os.MkdirAll(safePath, mode)` 递归创建\n273:   - 返回 `MkDirResponse{Path, Created: true}`\n274: - [ ] 12.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/mkdir_test.go`\n275: - [ ] 12.4 测试 `TestMkDir_CreateNew`：新目录创建成功，`created: true`\n276: - [ ] 12.5 测试 `TestMkDir_AlreadyExists`：目录已存在，`created: false`\n277: - [ ] 12.6 测试 `TestMkDir_CustomMode`：自定义 mode `0700` 被应用\n278: - [ ] 12.7 测试 `TestMkDir_PathIsFile`：路径是已有文件 → `ErrPathAlreadyExists`\n279: \n280: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestMkDir -v` 全部通过\n281: \n282: ---\n283: \n284: ## T13. 实现 SearchFiles（glob 模式搜索）\n285: \n286: - [ ] 13.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/search.go`\n287: - [ ] 13.2 实现 `SearchFiles(ctx context.Context, req *SearchFilesRequest) (*SearchFilesResponse, error)` 方法：\n288:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n289:   - 路径不存在返回 `ErrDirectoryNotFound`\n290:   - 路径不是目录返回 `ErrNotADirectory`\n291:   - `maxResults` 默认取 `fm.maxSearchResults`\n292:   - `filepath.WalkDir` 遍历目录树\n293:   - 计算深度 `depth = strings.Count(path, separator) - baseDepth`，超过 `maxSearchDepth` 则 `filepath.SkipDir`\n294:   - `path.Match(req.Pattern, d.Name())` 匹配文件名\n295:   - 匹配且非目录时添加到 `matches`\n296:   - `len(matches) >= maxResults` 时设置 `truncated: true` 并终止遍历\n297:   - 返回 `SearchFilesResponse{Matches, Truncated}`\n298: - [ ] 13.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/search_test.go`\n299: - [ ] 13.4 测试 `TestSearch_FindFiles`：glob 模式匹配到文件\n300: - [ ] 13.5 测试 `TestSearch_RecursiveGlob`：子目录中的文件也被匹配\n301: - [ ] 13.6 测试 `TestSearch_Truncated`：结果被 max_results 截断，`truncated: true`\n302: - [ ] 13.7 测试 `TestSearch_NoMatches`：无匹配结果，`truncated: false`\n303: - [ ] 13.8 测试 `TestSearch_RootNotFound`：搜索根目录不存在 → `ErrDirectoryNotFound`\n304: - [ ] 13.9 测试 `TestSearch_RootIsFile`：搜索根是文件 → `ErrNotADirectory`\n305: - [ ] 13.10 测试 `TestSearch_InvalidPattern`：无效 glob 模式 → 错误\n306: - [ ] 13.11 测试 `TestSearch_DepthLimit`：超过 MaxSearchDepth 的目录被跳过\n307: \n308: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestSearch -v` 全部通过\n309: \n310: ---\n311: \n312: ## T14. 实现 Chmod（权限修改）\n313: \n314: - [ ] 14.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/chmod.go`\n315: - [ ] 14.2 实现 `Chmod(ctx context.Context, req *ChmodRequest) (*ChmodResponse, error)` 方法：\n316:   - 解析八进制 mode 字符串（base 8）\n317:   - mode 格式无效返回 `ErrInvalidMode`\n318:   - mode > 0777 返回 `ErrModeOutOfRange`\n319:   - `sanitizePath(req.Path)` 校验路径\n320:   - 路径不存在返回 `ErrFileNotFound`\n321:   - `os.Chmod(safePath, parsedMode)` 修改权限\n322:   - 返回 `ChmodResponse{Path, Mode}`\n323: - [ ] 14.3 创建 `pkg/picod/files/chmod_test.go`\n324: - [ ] 14.4 测试 `TestChmod_ChangePermissions`：权限修改成功\n325: - [ ] 14.5 测试 `TestChmod_InvalidMode`：无效 mode 格式 → `ErrInvalidMode`\n326: - [ ] 14.6 测试 `TestChmod_ModeOutOfRange`：`\"07777\"` → `ErrModeOutOfRange`\n327: - [ ] 14.7 测试 `TestChmod_NotFound`：路径不存在 → `ErrFileNotFound`\n328: \n329: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/files/... -run TestChmod -v` 全部通过\n330: \n331: ---\n332: \n333: ## T15. 更新 Config 和 CLI 标志解析\n334: \n335: - [ ] 15.1 修改 `pkg/picod/config.go`：\n336:   - 在 `Config` 结构体中新增 `FileConfig FileConfig` 字段\n337:   - `ParseFlags()` 新增标志：`-max-chunk-size`（默认 `files.DefaultMaxChunkSize`）、`-max-batch-size`（默认 `files.DefaultMaxBatchSize`）、`-max-search-results`（默认 `files.DefaultMaxSearchResults`）、`-max-search-depth`（默认 `files.DefaultMaxSearchDepth`）\n338:   - 返回的 Config 包含 `FileConfig` 子结构\n339: - [ ] 15.2 修改 `pkg/picod/config_test.go`：\n340:   - 新增 `TestParseFlags_Defaults`：无标志 → 所有 file 相关字段为默认值\n341:   - 新增 `TestParseFlags_CustomFileLimits`：`--max-chunk-size=16777216 --max-batch-size=50` → 配置反映\n342:   - 新增 `TestParseFlags_CustomSearchLimits`：`--max-search-results=200 --max-search-depth=20` → 配置反映\n343: \n344: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestParseFlags -v` 全部通过；`go build ./pkg/picod/...` 编译通过\n345: \n346: ---\n347: \n348: ## T16. 更新 Server 路由注册\n349: \n350: - [ ] 16.1 修改 `pkg/picod/server.go`：\n351:   - 在 `Server` 结构体中新增 `fileManager files.FileManager` 字段\n352:   - `NewServer` 中调用 `files.NewFileManager(workspaceDir, config.FileConfig)` 初始化 fileManager\n353:   - `registerRoutes()` 更新路由注册：\n354:     - 保留 `api.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)`\n355:     - 新增 `fileGroup := api.Group(\"/files\")`\n356:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/read\", s.ReadFileHandler)`\n357:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/write\", s.WriteFileHandler)`\n358:     - `fileGroup.GET(\"/stat\", s.StatFileHandler)`\n359:     - `fileGroup.GET(\"\", s.ListFilesHandler)`\n360:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/upload\", s.UploadFileHandler)`\n361:     - `fileGroup.GET(\"/download\", s.DownloadFileHandler)`\n362:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/delete\", s.DeleteFileHandler)`\n363:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/move\", s.MoveFileHandler)`\n364:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/mkdir\", s.MkDirHandler)`\n365:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/search\", s.SearchFilesHandler)`\n366:     - `fileGroup.POST(\"/chmod\", s.ChmodHandler)`\n367:     - 保留 `s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)`\n368: - [ ] 16.2 在 `server.go` 中实现 HTTP Handler 桥接方法（将 Gin context 转换为 FileManager 调用）：\n369:   - `ReadFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `ReadFileRequest`，调用 `fileManager.ReadFile`，返回 JSON 响应\n370:   - `WriteFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `WriteFileRequest`，调用 `fileManager.WriteFile`，返回 JSON 响应\n371:   - `StatFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：从 `?path=` 查询参数获取路径，调用 `fileManager.StatFile`，返回 JSON 响应\n372:   - `ListFilesHandler(c *gin.Context)`：从 `?path=` 查询参数获取路径，调用 `fileManager.ListFiles`，返回 JSON 响应\n373:   - `UploadFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：检测 Content-Type，multipart → 表单处理，JSON → 绑定 `UploadFileRequest` 调用 `fileManager.UploadFile`\n374:   - `DownloadFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：从 `?path=` 查询参数获取路径，从 `Range` header 获取范围，调用 `fileManager.DownloadFile`，设置响应头并返回内容\n375:   - `DeleteFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `DeleteFileRequest`，调用 `fileManager.DeleteFile`，返回 JSON 响应\n376:   - `MoveFileHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `MoveFileRequest`，调用 `fileManager.MoveFile`，返回 JSON 响应\n377:   - `MkDirHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `MkDirRequest`，调用 `fileManager.MkDir`，返回 JSON 响应\n378:   - `SearchFilesHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `SearchFilesRequest`，调用 `fileManager.SearchFiles`，返回 JSON 响应\n379:   - `ChmodHandler(c *gin.Context)`：绑定 `ChmodRequest`，调用 `fileManager.Chmod`，返回 JSON 响应\n380: - [ ] 16.3 所有 Handler 的错误处理遵循统一格式：`{\"error\": \"<message>\", \"code\": <http_status_code>}`\n381: - [ ] 16.4 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n382: \n383: **Verification:** `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 零错误；所有 11 条文件管理路由已注册；`/health` 和 `/api/execute` 路由保持不变\n384: \n385: ---\n386: \n387: ## T17. 删除旧 files.go 并迁移遗留类型\n388: \n389: - [ ] 17.1 将 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中文件相关类型（`FileInfo`, `UploadFileRequest`, `FileEntry`, `ListFilesResponse`, `maxFileMode`）迁移或保留兼容性引用\n390: - [ ] 17.2 确认 `pkg/picod/files.go` 中所有逻辑已迁移至 `files/` 子包\n391: - [ ] 17.3 删除 `pkg/picod/files.go`\n392: - [ ] 17.4 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n393: - [ ] 17.5 运行 `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无告警\n394: \n395: **Verification:** `pkg/picod/files.go` 已删除；`go build ./pkg/picod/...` 零错误；`go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 无告警\n396: \n397: ---\n398: \n399: ## T18. Server 集成测试\n400: \n401: - [ ] 18.1 修改 `pkg/picod/server_test.go`：\n402:   - 新增 `TestServer_RoutesRegistered`：验证所有 11 条文件管理路由已注册\n403:   - 新增 `TestServer_LegacyRoutesRemoved`：`POST /api/files` → 404/400，`GET /api/files/*` → 404\n404:   - 新增 `TestServer_HealthCheck`：`/health` 返回 200\n405:   - 新增 `TestServer_AuthRequired`：无 JWT 请求 → 401\n406: - [ ] 18.2 创建 `pkg/picod/files/integration_test.go`：\n407:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_FileUploadDownload`：上传 → 列表验证 → 下载验证\n408:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_ReadWriteRoundTrip`：WriteFile → ReadFile → 内容一致\n409:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_DeleteAndVerify`：删除文件 → StatFile 返回 NotFound\n410:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_MoveAndVerify`：MoveFile → 原路径 NotFound，新路径 StatFile 成功\n411:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_SearchAfterCreate`：创建文件 → SearchFiles 匹配到\n412:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_ChmodAndStat`：Chmod → StatFile 验证 mode 变化\n413:   - 新增 `TestServer_Integration_PathTraversalBlocked`：所有端点均拒绝穿越路径\n414: - [ ] 18.3 测试辅助函数：\n415:   - `setupTestWorkspace(t *testing.T) (string, func())`：使用 `t.TempDir()`\n416:   - `createTestFile(t *testing.T, workspace, relPath, content string) string`：创建测试文件\n417:   - `newTestServer(t *testing.T, workspace string) *httptest.Server`：创建测试服务器\n418:   - `performJSONRequest(method, url string, body interface{}) *http.Response`：发送 JSON 请求\n419: \n420: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer_Integration -v` 全部通过；`go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer_Routes -v` 全部通过\n421: \n422: ---\n423: \n424: ## T19. 竞态检测与门禁验证\n425: \n426: - [ ] 19.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 编译通过\n427: - [ ] 19.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` 全部通过\n428: - [ ] 19.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` 无 data race 告警\n429: - [ ] 19.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 无 lint 警告\n430: - [ ] 19.5 运行 `go test -cover ./pkg/picod/...` 覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n431: - [ ] 19.6 确认 T/C 比率 > 0.4（测试代码行数 / 源代码行数）\n432: - [ ] 19.7 确认无 `log.Printf` 使用（仅允许 `klog`）\n433: - [ ] 19.8 确认日志中无敏感数据\n434: - [ ] 19.9 运行 `go mod tidy` 确保依赖正确\n435: - [ ] 19.10 确认每个 `*.go` 文件都有对应的 `*_test.go` 文件\n436: - [ ] 19.11 确认 AR-015 原有测试（execute, auth, health, config）仍全部通过\n437: \n438: **Verification:** 以上 11 项全部通过\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ## Task Dependencies\n443: \n444: ```\n445: T1 ──→ T2 ──→ T3 ──┬──→ T4 ──┐\n446:                     │          │\n447:                     ├──→ T5 ──┤\n448:                     │          │\n449:                     ├──→ T6 ──┤\n450:                     │          │\n451:                     ├──→ T7 ──┤\n452:                     │          │\n453:                     ├──→ T8 ──┤\n454:                     │          │\n455:                     ├──→ T9 ──┤\n456:                     │          │\n457:                     ├──→ T10 ─┤\n458:                     │          │\n459:                     ├──→ T11 ─┤\n460:                     │          │\n461:                     ├──→ T12 ─┤\n462:                     │          │\n463:                     ├──→ T13 ─┤\n464:                     │          │\n465:                     └──→ T14 ─┤\n466:                               │\n467: T1 ──→ T15 ───────────────────┤\n468:                               │\n469: T3 + T4..T14 + T15 ──→ T16 ──┤\n470:                               │\n471: T16 ──→ T17 ──────────────────┤\n472:                               │\n473: T17 ──→ T18 ──→ T19\n474: ```\n475: \n476: **Parallel execution opportunities:**\n477: - T2 (sanitizePath) can start after T1 (types/constants) is ready\n478: - T3 (FileManager constructor) depends on T1 and T2\n479: - T4-T14 (all file operation implementations) can run in parallel after T3 is ready — they all depend only on the FileManager interface and sanitizePath\n480: - T15 (Config extension) depends on T1 (FileConfig type defined)\n481: - T16 (Server route registration) depends on T3 (FileManager constructor) and T4-T14 (all handlers implemented)\n482: - T17 (Delete old files.go) depends on T16 (all routes working)\n483: - T18 (Integration tests) depends on T17 (clean codebase)\n484: - T19 (Gate verification) depends on T18\n485: \n486: ---\n487: \n488: ## Acceptance Criteria\n489: \n490: | # | Criterion | Command |\n491: |---|-----------|---------|\n492: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/picod/...` |\n493: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` |\n494: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` |\n495: | AC4 | 覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `go test -cover ./pkg/picod/...` |\n496: | AC5 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` |\n497: | AC6 | T/C 比率 > 0.4 | 代码行数统计 |\n498: | AC7 | POST /api/files/read 支持 offset/limit | `TestReadFile_WithOffsetAndLimit` 通过 |\n499: | AC8 | POST /api/files/write 支持 offset/append/overwrite | `TestWriteFile_Append` + `TestWriteFile_AtOffset` 通过 |\n500: | AC9 | GET /api/files/stat 返回完整元数据 | `TestStatFile_RegularFile` 通过 |\n501: | AC10 | POST /api/files/delete 支持单文件和批量删除 | `TestDelete_BatchAllSuccess` 通过 |\n502: | AC11 | POST /api/files/move 支持文件移动 | `TestMove_RenameFile` 通过 |\n503: | AC12 | POST /api/files/mkdir 支持递归创建目录 | `TestMkDir_CreateNew` 通过 |\n504: | AC13 | POST /api/files/search 支持 glob 模式 | `TestSearch_FindFiles` 通过 |\n505: | AC14 | POST /api/files/chmod 支持权限修改 | `TestChmod_ChangePermissions` 通过 |\n506: | AC15 | 上传支持分块传输 | `TestUpload_ChunkedMulti` 通过 |\n507: | AC16 | 下载支持 HTTP Range 请求 | `TestDownload_RangePartial` 通过 |\n508: | AC17 | 路径穿越返回 400 | `TestSanitizePath_ParentTraversal` 通过 |\n509: | AC18 | 文件不存在返回 404 | `TestReadFile_NotFound` 通过 |\n510: | AC19 | glob 搜索结果受 max_results 限制 | `TestSearch_Truncated` 通过 |\n511: | AC20 | 旧 files.go 已删除 | `ls pkg/picod/files.go` 返回不存在 |\n512: | AC21 | AR-015 原有测试仍通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestExecuteHandler -v` 通过 |\n513: | AC22 | 每个源文件有对应测试文件 | 文件列表检查 |\n514: | AC23 | 无 `log.Printf` 使用 | `rg 'log\\.Printf' pkg/picod/` 无结果 |\n515: | AC24 | 依赖清理 | `go mod tidy` 无变更 |\n\n(End of file - total 515 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/picod\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-016/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-016/design.md`, `design.md`, `delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 创建 files/ 子包脚手架、类型和常量\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/picod/files/` 目录\n- [ ] 1.2 创建 `pkg/picod/files/types.go`\n- [ ] 1.3 定义 `FileManager` 接口，包含 12 个方法：`ReadFile`, `WriteFile`, `StatFile`, `ListFiles`, `UploadFile`, `UploadFileChunked`, `DownloadFile`, `DeleteFile`, `MoveFile`, `MkDir`, `SearchFiles`, `Chmod`\n- [ ] 1.4 定义 `fileManager` 实现结构体，字段：`workspaceDir string`, `resolvedWorkspace string`, `maxChunkSize int64`, `maxBatchSize int`, `maxSearchResults int`, `maxSearchDepth int`, `tempDir string`\n- [ ] 1.5 定义请求/响应结构体：`ReadFileRequest`, `ReadFileResponse`, `WriteFileRequest`, `WriteFileResponse`, `StatFileResponse`, `ListFilesResponse`, `FileEntry`, `UploadFileRequest`, `ChunkedUploadRequest`, `DownloadFileRequest`, `DownloadFileResponse`, `DeleteFileRequest`, `DeleteFileResponse`, `DeleteFailure`, `MoveFileRequest`, `MoveFileResponse`, `MkDirRequest`, `MkDirResponse`, `SearchFilesRequest`, `SearchFilesResponse`, `ChmodRequest`, `ChmodResponse`（所有 JSON 标签与 design.md §2.3 一致）\n- [ ] 1.6 定义常量：`DefaultMaxChunkSize = 32 << 20`（33554432），`DefaultMaxBatchSize = 100`，`DefaultMaxSearchResults = 100`，`DefaultMaxSearchDepth = 50`，`DefaultDirMode = \"0755\"`，`DefaultFileMode = \"0644\"`，`MaxFileMode = 0777`，`ChunkExt = \".chunk\"`\n- [ ] 1.7 定义哨兵错误：`ErrPathTraversal`, `ErrFileNotFound`, `ErrDirectoryNotFound`, `ErrIsDirectory`, `ErrNotADirectory`, `ErrInvalidBase64`, `ErrInvalidMode`, `ErrModeOutOfRange`, `ErrChunkTooLarge`, `ErrRangeNotSatisfiable`, `ErrBatchSizeExceeded`, `ErrDirectoryNotEmpty`, `ErrPathAlreadyExists`, `ErrWorkspaceNotInitialized`\n- [ ] 1.8 定义 `FileConfig` 结构体（用于 config.go 扩展），字段：`MaxChunkSize int64`, `MaxBatchSize int`, `MaxSearchResults int`, `MaxSearchDepth int`\n- [ ] 1.9 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-016/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775846813199,"end":1775846813206}}}}
